\section*{Parafollicular cell (C-cell)}

Part of follicular epithelium or in clusters between follicles.
- Larger than follicular cells, less stained.
- Little amount of rER, long mitochondria, and large golgi. Contain granules with hormone.
- Synthesize calcitonin....lowers blood calcium levels by inhibiting osteoclast activity.

